ry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f58359dc9014e9f9ddac091457ee082d42f7d39","tid":1831030,"uid":2377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T06:54:55.000Z","msg":"只要有心任何人都係義士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nrebag"},{"pid":"57f9a5120c7ab9b2a4b04209e2209230eadc7d10","tid":1831030,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T06:55:56.000Z","msg":"最新 update<br />\n<br />\nJanuary 21, 2020<br />\n紅磡:龍門冰室 x 香港人嘅冰室資源分享中心<br />\n黃埔年宵後續．九號水產年宵市集<br />\n元朗恐襲半週年 和理跑<br />\n1p 觀塘和你寫揮春<br />\n1p 長沙灣x荔枝角 和你Lunch<br />\n2p 荔枝角:香城年宵新年市集<br />\n4p 大埔醫院:醫護界街站<br />\n5:30p 北角:新公務員工會街站<br />\n6p 旺角:和理過年&bull;宵市集<br />\n6p 炮台山:香港製藥及醫療儀器業職工總會招募會員街站<br />\n6:30p 荔枝角:二百萬三罷聯合陣線 宣傳街站<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">7p 杏花邨:元朗黑夜半週年靜坐<br />\n7p 銅鑼灣站:721恐襲半週年靜坐<br />\n7:30p 柴灣:元朗黑夜半週年靜坐</span><br />\n8p 121元朗黑夜半週年<br />\n<br />\nRef : <br />\n<a href=\"https://hkrev.info/march.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkrev.info%2Fmarch.php&d=%2F7nbYOXxgzDTTn%2FAx8VV995k9s62d79lhUbErROZgj4%3D&h=d58b8aae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkrev.info/march.php</a>"}]}